{
  "id": "665bc3b8146fed001c04890f",
  "title": "安積山影さへ見ゆる山の井の浅くは人を思ふものかは",
  "created": 1717289915,
  "updated": 1717291285,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "665bc3db5e90c000000e62c7",
      "text": "安積山影さへ見ゆる山の井の浅くは人を思ふものかは",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289947,
      "updated": 1717290001
    },
    {
      "id": "665bc3bb5e90c000000e62b7",
      "text": "[古今集仮名序]に見える歌",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289915,
      "updated": 1717291285
    },
    {
      "id": "665bc3bb5e90c000000e62b8",
      "text": " >[安積山]の言葉は、[采女]の[戯れ]よりよみて、この二歌は、歌の父母のやうにてぞ手習ふ人の初めにもしける",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289915,
      "updated": 1717289915
    },
    {
      "id": "665bc3bb5e90c000000e62b9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289915,
      "updated": 1717289915
    },
    {
      "id": "665bc3bb5e90c000000e62ba",
      "text": "他出文献",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289915,
      "updated": 1717289915
    },
    {
      "id": "665bc3bb5e90c000000e62bb",
      "text": " [万葉集]巻16、3807では四句五句が異なる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289915,
      "updated": 1717289940
    },
    {
      "id": "665bc3bb5e90c000000e62bc",
      "text": "  >[安積山影さへみゆる山の井の浅き心を我が思はなくに]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289915,
      "updated": 1717289915
    },
    {
      "id": "665bc3bb5e90c000000e62bd",
      "text": "  [左注]では",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289915,
      "updated": 1717289915
    },
    {
      "id": "665bc3bb5e90c000000e62be",
      "text": "   [葛城王]が[陸奥国]に遣わされた時、国司が非礼をしたために接待を楽しまずにいた。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289915,
      "updated": 1717289915
    },
    {
      "id": "665bc3bb5e90c000000e62bf",
      "text": "   そこで[采女]が左手に杯を、右手に水を持って王の膝をたたいてこの歌を詠んだという",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289915,
      "updated": 1717289915
    },
    {
      "id": "665bc3bb5e90c000000e62c0",
      "text": " [『大和物語』]155段にもこの歌が載っているらしい",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289915,
      "updated": 1717289915
    },
    {
      "id": "665bc3bb5e90c000000e62c1",
      "text": "  [『十訓抄』]にも載る",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289915,
      "updated": 1717289915
    },
    {
      "id": "665bc3bb5e90c000000e62c2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289915,
      "updated": 1717289915
    },
    {
      "id": "665bc3bb5e90c000000e62c3",
      "text": "[浅香山の歌]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289915,
      "updated": 1717289915
    },
    {
      "id": "665bc3bb5e90c000000e62c4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289915,
      "updated": 1717289915
    },
    {
      "id": "665bc3bb5e90c000000e62c5",
      "text": "　[安積山]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289915,
      "updated": 1717289915
    },
    {
      "id": "665bc3bb5e90c000000e62c6",
      "text": "　[山の井]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1717289915,
      "updated": 1717289915
    }
  ]
}